(75, 45, 1, 'Cochin - Munnar (130 kms / 04 hrs)\r\nYou are greeted on arrival at Cochin International Airport /Railway station by Munnar Holidays representative and thereafter depart for enjoying the scenic beauty & the marvelous waterfalls, high mountains with the low flying clouds passing by. Arrive Munnar and check in at Resort. Day at Leisure. Overnight at Munnar.', '2018-11-02 15:04:53', '2018-11-02 19:04:53'),
(76, 45, 2, 'Morning after breakfast proceed for sightseeing in Munnar which includes visit to the flower garden and for an elephant safari, before driving on to the scenic Mattupetty dam, Eco- point and Kundala dam areas. At Kundala dam there is an opportunity to enjoy boating on the lake. Finally we drive through a vegetable growing area to Top station which is situated high in the mountains on the border between Tamil Nadu and Kerala. After Lunch Proceed on time to board your flight/train with sweet memories of your holiday.Evening proceed to cochin.drop at kochin.', '2018-11-02 15:04:53', '2018-11-02 19:04:53'),
