(169, 87, 6, 'Mysore-Sreerangapatana\r\nAfter breakfast and fresh up check out proceed to Visit Srirangapattanam \r\nRanganathaswamy Temple, \r\nWater jail\r\nSummer Palace\r\nThriveni sangamam\r\nAfter lunch visit Mysore palace and Philomena church Chamundi temple after Dinner Back hometown', '2019-04-06 06:53:28', '2019-04-06 10:53:28'),
(170, 88, 1, 'Starting from Cochin International Airport at morning  8\'o clock 26th December 18.\r\nArrival at Hyderabad airport our friendly Driver/tour manager will meet you. Pick up & transfer to Golconda fort after the Visit Proceed to the hotel, Check in to the hotel.\r\nAfter Fresh-n-up and Lunch at the Hotel, We will proceed to the Snow world. Then Afterwards a city breaks tour. We will visit Lumbini Park this evening, walk through the alleyways and a real treat for your eyes the laser show, following a boating to the Buddha statue in Husain Sagar lake. The group proceeds to room around 20.00. Overnight stay at the hotel.', '2018-11-15 11:24:15', '2018-11-15 16:24:15'),
(171, 88, 2, 'Ramoji film city\r\nThe morning we leave to Ramoji film city @08.00 after breakfast.\r\nRamoji film city is the fastest growing tourist destination in Hyderabad. Enjoy your day here and witness the location of your favorite movies. Also, Experience the Winter Carnival with the\r\nChristmas Celebrations. After the visit return to the hotel @18.00 and rest of the day is at your comfort.', '2018-11-15 11:24:15', '2018-11-15 16:24:15'),
(172, 88, 3, 'After the breakfast, Check-out & Today we will proceed to explore Shah’s Hyderabad. Visit Birla Mandir, Charminar, Mecca Masjid, And After Lunch Visit Salarjung museum. Enjoy the day and visit the famous avenues for shopping pearls. & Later Drop at Airport and Board Flight for Back to Cochin.', '2018-11-15 11:24:15', '2018-11-15 16:24:15'),
(173, 89, 1, 'Pic up from manglore railway stationMorning Arrival at Kudag (Coorg)  after fresh up and proceed to sightsee.\r\n* Abbey Falls\r\n* Nisargadhama\r\n* Barapole River\r\nOver night stay in Coorg.', '2018-11-15 10:25:30', '2018-11-15 15:25:30'),
(174, 89, 2, 'Coorg – Mysore -( 2 h 45 min 108.1 km)\r\nProceed to Mysore enjoy the scenic beauty of via NH275on the way visit Namdroling Monastery Bylakuppe.\r\nReach Mysore and check in to the hotel and night stay.', '2018-11-15 10:25:30', '2018-11-15 15:25:30'),
(175, 89, 3, 'Mysore  sightseeing \r\n* Mysore palace \r\n* Philomena church\r\n* Chamundi temple \r\n* Mysore palace\r\n* Zoo \r\n* Vrindavan garden with music fountain\r\nMysore and check in to the hotel and night stay.', '2018-11-15 10:25:30', '2018-11-15 15:25:30'),
