(178, 89, 6, 'After breakfast and Check out and proceed to hometown', '2018-11-15 10:25:30', '2018-11-15 15:25:30'),
(179, 91, 1, 'On your arrival at Calicut Airport/ Railway station meet our representative and drive to Wayanad(80 Kms) the extraordinary destination of Kerala with a bundle of attractions as well as it’s an experience in the lap of Nature for every traveler. Check in your hotel, have leisure and overnight stay near edakal caves', '2018-11-15 10:23:41', '2018-11-15 15:23:41'),
(180, 91, 2, 'After breakfast proceeds to the wild Wayanad as you can visit Edakkal caves which are situated on the top of Ambukkuthimala with a view of three states as well as the spot has many carvings of the stone age and one should truck and climb the hill to reach the cave...\r\nAfter lunch visit Soojippara Waterfall one of the major spots in Wayanad as a typical natural fall where you can take bath and enjoy a lot. Then Proceed to Banasura as it’s known as the largest earth Dam in India with the fabulous view of river Banasura and evergreen vegetation. Afternoon you can visit Pookot Lake, one of the best- maintained picnic spots in Wayanad with amble facilities for boating and other recreational activities, Overnight stays.', '2018-11-15 10:23:41', '2018-11-15 15:23:41'),
(181, 91, 3, 'Kuruwa and Muthanga- Mysore(2 hours- 100km)\r\nCheck out from the hotel after breakfast and proceed to today ’s your sightseeing. It will be at Kuruwa island as it’s known as the largest island created by the river Kabani with the fabulous view of Forest and evergreen vegetation. Afternoon you can visit the Muthanga\r\nwildlife sanctuary, with Exiting jeep and other recreational activities. Later, then evening proceed to Mysore.you can enjoy the wildlife beauty along with the travel. Check in to the hotel at Mysore and overnight stay at Mysore.', '2018-11-15 10:23:41', '2018-11-15 15:23:41'),
(182, 91, 4, 'After breakfast, proceed to Mysore sightseeing visit the Chamundi temple, zoo, st.philomina in the morning then afternoon proceed to zoo and Vrindavan garden. Get back to the hotel and overnight stay at the hotel.', '2018-11-15 10:23:41', '2018-11-15 15:23:41'),
(183, 91, 5, 'Mysore-Sreerangapatana- Bangalore (2.30hrs-130km)\r\nAfter breakfast and check out proceed towards Bangalore. Visit Srirangapattanam - \r\nRanganathaswamy Temple, Dariya Daulat, Gumbuz, Sangam, Tipu’s Death Place, Thriveni sangamam then proceed to Bangalore at evening drop at Bangalore airport or Railway\r\nstation.', '2018-11-15 10:23:41', '2018-11-15 15:23:41'),
(184, 92, 1, 'After reaching Mysore, Check in to the hotel after fresh up and breakfast then start your journey enjoy the sightings of \r\nMysore Palace - an architectural marvel, \r\nKrishnarajasagar Dam & Brindavan Gardens \r\nSt. Philomena Church- erected in Gothic style \r\nChamundi Hills. Overnight stay.', '2019-01-31 06:04:19', '2019-01-31 11:04:19'),
(185, 92, 2, 'After Breakfast checkout and proceed to the Zoo.\r\nAfter lunch proceeds to Sreeranga Pattana.Visit the See Ranganathan temple\r\nTippu Palace\r\nThe tomb of Tippu\r\nTriveni Sangamam. \r\nAfter dinner proceed to Ooty (6-hour travel 250 km)\r\nOvernight travel to Ooty.', '2019-01-31 06:04:19', '2019-01-31 11:04:19'),
(186, 92, 3, 'Check in to hotel After fresh up and breakfast. Journey to Ooty “the Queen of hill stations’. On arrival, check into the hotel. The day is booked for exploring the beauty of Ooty. Visit the Botanical Gardens- with a peaceful Lotus Pond then cover Dodda Betta. Other attractions\r\nare the \r\nTea estates \r\nLambs Rock\r\nDolphins Nose (a picnic spot), \r\nOoty Lake, \r\nEvening proceeds to the hometown.', '2019-01-31 06:04:19', '2019-01-31 11:04:19'),
(187, 93, 1, 'Arrival at Coimbatore Airport meet our representative and transfer to Ooty. Enjoy the panoramic view en route. Reach Ooty and Check in at Pre – Booked Hotel. Rest of the Day at leisure. \r\n\r\nDinner & Overnight stay.', '2018-12-28 08:29:59', '2018-12-28 13:29:59'),
(188, 93, 2, 'Ooty Sightseeing\r\nAfter breakfast proceed Ooty Sightseeing; \r\nvisit Coonoor, \r\nSim’s Park,\r\nLambs Rock & Dolphin’s Nose. \r\nDinner & Overnight stay.', '2018-12-28 08:29:59', '2018-12-28 13:29:59'),
(189, 93, 3, 'After having your sumptuous Breakfast, proceed for today’s Sightseeing \r\nDoddabetta Peak (Highest Point of Nilgiris Hills), \r\nDeerpark, Kamraj Sagar Dam & Avalanche Lake.,\r\nDinner & Overnight stay.', '2018-12-28 08:29:59', '2018-12-28 13:29:59'),
(190, 93, 4, 'Ooty – Kodaikanal (250km 6 hours)\r\nThe morning after healthy breakfast proceed to Ooty Coonoor toy train after the memorable journey proceeds to Kodaikanal enjoying Panoramic views en route. \r\nEvening at leisure. Dinner & Overnight stay.', '2018-12-28 08:29:59', '2018-12-28 13:29:59'),
(191, 93, 5, 'Kodaikanal Sightseeing\r\nToday after breakfast proceed for Kodaikanal sightseeing visit\r\nKodaikanal Lake,\r\nCoaker’s Walk,\r\nKurinji Andavar Temple, \r\nDolphins Nose, \r\nChettiyar Park, \r\nPamber Falls, \r\nPillar Rock, \r\nThalaiyar Falls,\r\nDinner & Overnight stay.', '2018-12-28 08:29:59', '2018-12-28 13:29:59'),
(192, 93, 6, 'Kodaikanal - Coimbatore Departure\r\nOn the last day of our tour, \r\nWe will have breakfast in the morning and check out from the hotel to drive back to Coimbatore.\r\nTransferred to the airport and board your flight to onward Destination.', '2018-12-28 08:29:59', '2018-12-28 13:29:59'),
(207, 36, 2, 'Alleppey - cochin (55km1.15Hrs)\r\nAfter breakfast proceeds to Alleppey Houseboat/Hotel, Full day at disposal. Overnight stay at houseboat/Hotel in Alleppey. Enjoy the beauty of backwater and refresh the mind.', '2019-11-17 06:57:38', '2019-11-17 11:57:38'),
(208, 36, 1, 'On arrival in Cochin Airport, our cab will pick you up & transfer to the hotel in Kochi, after refreshment local sightseeing at Kochi\r\n* Mattancherry\r\n* Marine Drive', '2019-11-17 06:57:38', '2019-11-17 11:57:38'),
(229, 98, 1, 'Morning Arrival at Kudag (Coorg)  after fresh up and Breakfast proceed to sightsee.\r\n* Abbey Falls\r\n* Nisargadhama\r\n* Barapole River', '2018-11-15 10:19:53', '2018-11-15 15:19:53'),
(230, 98, 2, 'Proceed to Mysore enjoy the scenic beauty of Coorg – Mysore route. 2 h 45 min (108.1 km) via NH275on the way visit Namdroling Monastery Bylakuppe .Reach Mysore and check in to the hotel and night stay.', '2018-11-15 10:19:53', '2018-11-15 15:19:53'),
(231, 98, 3, 'Mysore  sightseeing \r\n* Mysore palace \r\n* Philomena church\r\n* Chamundi temple \r\n* Mysore palace\r\n* Zoo \r\n* Vrindavan garden', '2018-11-15 10:19:53', '2018-11-15 15:19:53'),
(232, 98, 4, 'Proceed to Sreerangapattana and visit\r\n* Ranganathan temple \r\n* Water jail \r\n* Summer palace\r\n* Thriveni and Gumbaz\r\n\r\n Proceed to Bangalore to Bangalore, 2 h 55 min (145.4 km)\r\novernight stay in Banglore', '2018-11-15 10:19:53', '2018-11-15 15:19:53'),
(233, 98, 5, 'After fresh up and Breakfast proceed to Bangalore Sightseeing Bangalore.\r\n* Bangalore palace\r\n* Lal bag\r\n* UB city/forum mall\r\nCommercial street for purchase\r\nOvernight stay.', '2018-11-15 10:19:53', '2018-11-15 15:19:53'),
(234, 98, 6, 'After breakfast and Check out and proceed to hometown.', '2018-11-15 10:19:53', '2018-11-15 15:19:53'),
(245, 99, 2, 'After buffet lunch at an Indian restaurant, we proceed to check in at the hotel, Kuala Lumpur. Time for rest (One Hour), after we proceed for City Tour, Enjoy the blend of garden city charm, old world Moorish architecture and other famous landmarks of this vibrant modern capital of Malaysia.\r\n\r\nInteresting sights include KL’s trademark sultan Abdul Samad Building, Independence Square, Lake Gardens, Parliament House National Monument, King’s Palace.\r\n\r\nAfter finishing City tour we spend time for the shopping at China Town / Central Market Mall / Hanifa Shopping center. A night view photo stops at Twin Tower (Petronas Twin Tower) and Visit the Observation Deck (422 M Height) of KL Tower.\r\n\r\nBuffet Dinner at Indian Restaurant. Overnight stay at Hotel, Kuala Lumpur.', '2018-11-15 10:16:12', '2018-11-15 15:16:12'),
(246, 99, 3, 'After Breakfast, Check out from the Hotel, then proceed to Singapore from Genting Highlands, Malaysia. \r\n\r\nBuffet Lunch at Restaurant, Johor Bahru.\r\n\r\nReach Singapore @ 14:00 Hrs (approximately), Check in at the Hotel, Singapore. Then we proceed for Tour Garden by the bay.', '2018-11-15 10:16:12', '2018-11-15 15:16:12'),
(247, 99, 4, 'After breakfast, proceed for the half day Singapore City Tour – Singapore Cricket Club, Historic Parliament House, National Gallery. The gallery consists of two national monuments former supreme court building, and city hall – Photo stop here and view these magnificent buildings up close (depends on weather conditions).\r\n\r\nAnother attraction is Merlion Park and enjoys an impressive view of Marina Bay. The Merlion, a mythological creature that is part lion & part fish. \r\n\r\nBuffet Lunch at Indian Restaurant.\r\n\r\nAfter lunch then proceeds to Sentosa sunset tour with island admission, Cable car ride, Sea aquarium and Wings of Time 2nd Show. Sentosa is an island resort off Singapore’s southern coast, connected to the city by road, cable car, pedestrian boardwalk, and monorail. By Sentosa station, Tiger Sky Tower has panoramic views that can stretch as far as Indonesia. On the south coast, Palawan Beach is lined with food stalls, bars and has a suspension bridge to a small offshore island. Palm-lined, crescent-shaped Tanjong Beach is more tranquil. Enter and explore the marine realm of S.E.A. Aquarium, home to more than 100,000 marine animals of over 800 species, across into 49 different habitats, each one as fascinating as the next.\r\nIt’s an experience you won’t forget. Spanning several exotic vistas and across the fabric of time, Wings Of Time is a multi-sensory extravaganza that tells an epic tale of courage, mystery, and magic brought to you an internationally acclaimed team. The first of its kind, Wings of Time is the only permanent night show in the world set in the open sea. Set against a signature backdrop and a larger-than-life water screen, audiences can look forward to a contemporary storyline weaved together with an epic experiential fusion of the latest multimedia effects, including 3D projection mapping, state-of-the-art lasers, robotic water fountains and giant water jets, pyrotechnics. Created and produced by a team of local and international entertainment experts, Wings of Time is a night extravaganza of majestic proportions that is bound to captivate and wow every guest.\r\n\r\nBuffet Dinner, Overnight stay at Hotel, Singapore.', '2018-11-15 10:16:12', '2018-11-15 15:16:12'),
(248, 99, 5, 'SINGAPORE\r\n\r\nAfter Breakfast, Then proceed for Full Day Universal Studio\r\n\r\nLunch at Universal Studio,\r\nBuffet dinner, Overnight stay at hotel,', '2018-11-15 10:16:12', '2018-11-15 15:16:12'),
(249, 99, 6, 'After Breakfast, proceed for the Jurong Bird Park Tour. Opened in 1971, millions of bird lovers from around the world have experienced our colorful avian world. Jurong Bird Park is Singapore’s first wildlife park and Asia’s largest bird park, offering a 20.2-hectare hillside haven for more than 5,000 birds across 400 species –– of which 15% are threatened. The park’s goal is simple, we hope to enhance visitor\'s understanding and appreciation of our feathered residents through naturalistic exhibits, interactive feeding sessions, and world-class bird shows.\r\n\r\nBuffet Lunch at Indian Restaurant.\r\n\r\nAfter Lunch, we spend the time for Singapore shopping at Mustafa (Little India), Finish all our Shopping, Pickup from Meeting Point at 16:00 Hrs. drop at Singapore International\r\nAirport with wonderful Memories.\r\n\r\nMI 468 Singapore Departure 20:10 Hrs. | Cochin Arrival 22:05Hrs.', '2018-11-15 10:16:12', '2018-11-15 15:16:12'),
(250, 100, 1, 'Pick up from Calicut and proceed to Wayanad, breakfast will be served at on the way. Proceed to sightseeing,\r\nLakkidi viewpoint\r\nChain tree\r\nPookkode lake\r\nBanasura Dam\r\nMeenmutty Falls\r\nEdakkal Caves\r\nCheck in to hotel and overnight stay\r\nBuffet Dinner and lunch will be provided in the right time.', '2019-07-28 16:45:11', '2019-07-28 20:45:11'),
(251, 100, 2, 'After breakfast, Proceed to Kuruva dweeps enjoy the waterfalls and forest till noon \r\nafter lunch proceeds to Soochipara Falls.\r\nEvening drop at Calicut.', '2019-07-28 16:45:11', '2019-07-28 20:45:11'),
(252, 90, 1, 'Our campground is situated over the western ghats, Munnar... there are many tribal villages, so much of trekking places are nearby our campsite especially Meesapullimala- the second highest peak in the western ghats of Idukki district. Starting from Suryanelli, enjoy the off-road jeep safari to Kolukkumalai. Explore the beauty of nature blend with the exotic climatic condition. Experience the campfire and dinner overnight stay in a tent', '2019-09-17 04:56:36', '2019-09-17 08:56:36'),
(253, 90, 2, 'Local Site seeing and jeep safaris are available from our campground especially to overnight (tea factory located in the world\'s highest organic tea estate) .our campsite is surrounded by eucalyptus off-road trekking – phantom head you can also watch the sunrise and Aanai Idukki dam from our site which would a pleasing experience.  Evening back to the camping area and overnight stay in a tent.', '2019-09-17 04:56:36', '2019-09-17 08:56:36'),
(254, 101, 1, 'Reach at Ernakulam junction railway station/ Airport by morning, After Breakfast Proceeds to Alappuzha,  by 10 am you will reach alapuzha and enter to the boat  after fresh up and a small nap in  the boat ride will start at 12 pm\r\nStay at House Boat.', '2019-03-02 09:50:51', '2019-03-02 14:50:51'),
(255, 101, 2, 'Morning breakfast and check out then proceed to kochi enjoy the jewis synagogue and street then have a small walk in marrainedrive.. then after lunch proceed to munnar 3 hour journey then chek in to resort at 5 pm\r\nAnd enjoy the resort facilities', '2019-03-02 09:50:51', '2019-03-02 14:50:51'),
(256, 101, 3, 'Munnar Local SightSeeing After breakfast proceeds for Rajamalai (Eravikulam) National Park – famous for Nilgiri Tahr (Wild goat), Anaimudi Peak – South India’s Highest Peak, Tata Tea Museum, Historical Church, Mattupetty, Echo Point, Kundala Lake, Photo Point, \r\nSpice Plantation. Overnight stay at the Treehouse Resort in munnar', '2019-03-02 09:50:51', '2019-03-02 14:50:51'),
(257, 101, 4, 'After breakfast, proceed to Athirapalli, the exotic Waterfalls  destination of Kerala. It’s also known as the Niagra falls of the state. You can enjoy a beautiful journey through the hills and valleys of Western Ghat to reach this jungle destination, also you can enjoy the dips in the river if the climate permits.', '2019-03-02 09:50:51', '2019-03-02 14:50:51'),
(258, 102, 1, 'Arrival at Hyderabad airport morning after check-in \r\nthe hotel.\r\nvisit Birla Mandir, Snow world, Lumbini park, Hussain\r\nSagar Lake & Lesser show.\r\nOvernight Stay.', '2019-10-14 10:40:30', '2019-10-14 14:40:30'),
(259, 102, 2, 'After breakfast proceeds to Ramoji Film City –night stay.', '2019-10-14 10:40:30', '2019-10-14 14:40:30'),
(260, 102, 3, 'After breakfast continue sightseeing of Hyderabad.\r\n(Old City) City Salar Jung Museum,Charminar,Makkah Masjid,Chowmahalla,Palace, Golkonda fort.\r\ncheck out from the hotel and drop at Airport.', '2019-10-14 10:40:30', '2019-10-14 14:40:30'),
(261, 103, 1, 'Meals – dinner\r\n\r\nArrival Delhi In The Morning by Air/Train. Pick up by car and proceed to Shimla On the Way visit Pinjore Garden Timber Trail Dinner at Hotel', '2019-07-24 07:48:26', '2019-07-24 11:48:26'),
(262, 103, 2, 'Shimla Local Sightseeing-  Manali \r\nMeals – Breakfast and dinner\r\nToday morning after breakfast visit Kufri which includes, (Green valley, Mini zoo, Adventure park, and  Fagu valley). In the evening return back to Shimla where you can visit Mall Road, Ridge, Scandal Point, Lakkar Bazaar, Christ church, and Lower Bazaar and proceed to Manali reach Manali by a late evening around 10-11pm dinner from the hotel.', '2019-07-24 07:48:26', '2019-07-24 11:48:26'),
(263, 103, 3, 'Manali Local Sightseeing\r\nMeals – Breakfast and dinner\r\nAfter fresh up, proceed to city tour of Manali which includes:- \r\n1. Hadimba Devi Temple:-  It chief central of interest in Manali, dedicated to the goddess Hadimba, the Wife of Bheema of Mahabharata Fame, This is a wooden temple, In the dense forest of magnificent deodar, is about 2.5kms from the Mall. It is a pleasant stroll to the temple which was built in 1553 A.D.\r\n 2. Vashisht(3.5kms from Mall):- Hot Sulphur Water springs –  which is widely believed as effective skin diseases healer and possess various medical properties. Nearby it is the pyramidal stone temple dedicated to Vashisht Muni & lord Rama temple.\r\n   \r\n3. Tibetan-Monastery(0.5 Kms)  This  Gadhan Thekchoking Gompa dominates the Tibetan area builtin  1969. The main attraction of the monastery is the handicrafts of Tibetan artistry and the carpets that are woven and sold in the monastery\r\n 4. Club House (2 Kms from Mall):- Clubhouse is famous for amusement activities like skating, Discotheque, auditorium, etc.\r\n Later in the evening free to explore the Shopping Malls (Mall Road & IBEX Market) of Manali. Dinner & Overnight at hotel', '2019-07-24 07:48:26', '2019-07-24 11:48:26'),
(264, 103, 4, 'Rothang pass Solang Valley \r\nMeals – Breakfast and dinner\r\nAfter breakfast visit to Rohtang & Solang Valley (on the way) and, Enjoy skiing, paragliding and other adventurous activities (Cost not included),  Return to the hotel by evening, Dinner and Overnight stay at Hotel', '2019-07-24 07:48:26', '2019-07-24 11:48:26'),
(265, 103, 5, 'Meals – Breakfast.\r\nAfter breakfast in the morning, check out the hotel and proceed to Delhi In Late evening Drop At Delhi Airport/Railways station/hotel in Delhi by a late evening around 11 pm.', '2019-07-24 07:48:26', '2019-07-24 11:48:26'),
(266, 104, 1, 'Pickup from Hyderabad airport around 10.30am. on the way visit Golconda fort,\r\n\r\nAfter lunch check-in to the hotel and fresh-up  proceed for sightseeing in\r\n•	Snow world, \r\n•	Lumbini Park,\r\n•	Hussainsagar lake \r\n•	Lesser show –', '2019-10-14 10:39:24', '2019-10-14 14:39:24'),
(267, 104, 2, 'After breakfast proceeds to Ramoji Film City.\r\nindia\'s biggest and well-known film making center and you can enjoy a  whole day in a wonderful place\r\nafter sightseeing back to the hotel and overnight stay at Hyderabad', '2019-10-14 10:39:24', '2019-10-14 14:39:24'),
(268, 104, 3, 'After breakfast Check out from the hotel visit \r\n•	Birla Mandir, Charminar, \r\n•	Salarjung Museum, \r\n•	Chowmahalla Palace, \r\n•	Mecca masjid & shopping – \r\n drop at Airport', '2019-10-14 10:39:24', '2019-10-14 14:39:24'),
(269, 105, 1, 'On arrival at Srinagar, you will be met by our representative and transfer you to Hotel.\r\nIn the evening, go for a Shikara Ride at Dal Lake, overnight stay & dinner at the Hotel in Srinagar', '2019-10-06 08:36:17', '2019-10-06 12:36:17'),
(270, 105, 2, 'Srinagar - Gulmarg-Srinagar \r\nAfter breakfast leaves Srinagar and drives to Gulmarg which is one of the most beautiful summer resort in the valley. It is also popular for its golf course (in summer), the highest in the world and skiing during the winter season. Enjoy the splendor of nature and the snowy mountains. One can have Gondola ride (cable car) ride there, and back to Srinagar, overnight stay & dinner at the Hotel in Srinagar', '2019-10-06 08:36:17', '2019-10-06 12:36:17'),
(271, 105, 3, 'Srinagar - Sonmarg- Srinagar \r\nLeave for Sonmarg after breakfast. Visit Rafting point and Wayela point en route spend the rest of your day at leisure/ back to Srinagar.overnight stay & dinner at the Hotel in Srinagar', '2019-10-06 08:36:17', '2019-10-06 12:36:17'),
(272, 105, 4, 'Pahalgam 2440 Mtrs (vale of Kashmir) on the way visit Saffron fields, Avantipur ruins, and Anantnag Sulpher spring. Pahalgam is the most famous place for Indian Film Industry. Enjoy the nature charm of the valley, and back to Srinagar, overnight stay & dinner at the Hotel in Srinagar', '2019-10-06 08:36:17', '2019-10-06 12:36:17'),
(273, 105, 5, 'Srinagar-Dodhpather-Srinagar \r\nAfter breakfast leave to Srinagar and drive to Doodhpathri. Doodhpathri (translation; Valley of Milk), It is a beautiful meadow with sheep grazing around and pools of water add to the beauty of the vast green pasture. The background with snow-capped mountains and silver-white clouds hung in the blue sky is mesmerizing. and back to Srinagar, overnight stay & dinner at the Hotel in Srinagar', '2019-10-06 08:36:17', '2019-10-06 12:36:17'),
(274, 105, 6, 'Srinagar \r\nAfter breakfast visit to Mughal Gardens, Nishat Bagh, Shalimar Bagh, Pari Mahal, shankaracharia Temple, Dal Lake. Afternoon transfer in time to the airport to connect onwards destination flight.      \r\nBid adieu to the picturesque valley as you leave for home with wonderful memories', '2019-10-06 08:36:17', '2019-10-06 12:36:17'),
(275, 106, 1, 'On arrival at Alappuzha, you will be entered to the  Houseboat at 11 am .with a welcome drink. Enjoy the beauty of Kuttanad and Vembanad Enjoy the lunch with Chromide (Karimeen) & chicken curry\r\nevening tea & Snacks check out from the boat with sweet memories', '2019-10-10 11:16:05', '2019-10-10 15:16:05'),
(276, 107, 1, 'Delhi - Manali (by Volvo)\r\nArrival at Delhi pickup from the airport and transfer to R K Ashram Metro Station at Volvo Boarding Point Volvo Start at 5:30 PM From Delhi to Manali over Night Journey in Volvo. The next day reaches Manali.', '2019-10-10 13:08:56', '2019-10-10 17:08:56'),
(277, 107, 2, 'Manali Arrival (Local Sightseeing)\r\nOn arrival at Manali, our representative assists to transfer you to the pre-booked hotel. Check-in at the hotel, freshen up and enjoy leisure time at the comfort of your room. After Some time enjoy the city tour visiting some of the prominent spots and attractions including Hadimba Devi Temple also called Dhungri Temple, Manu Temple, Tibetan Monastery and Vashisth Village. After enjoying an exciting tour of Manali city return back by afternoon and enjoy your free will (reserved for leisure). Dinner and Overnight stay will be at the hotel in Manali.', '2019-10-10 13:08:56', '2019-10-10 17:08:56'),
(278, 107, 3, 'Manali (Full day Trip to Rohtang Pass )\r\nEnjoy the morning breakfast at the hotel and later get ready for an excursion to visit Rohtang Pass is outstandingly beautiful and is an ideal spot to view the majestic snow-covered Himalayas, serene natural surroundings, pristine lake, and fairy white snow round the year. Return back to the hotel on time for dinner and overnight stay.', '2019-10-10 13:08:56', '2019-10-10 17:08:56'),
(279, 107, 4, 'Manali (Full Day Trip to Kullu Naggar – Delhi by Volvo\r\nEnjoy the morning breakfast at the hotel and later get ready for an excursion to visit Naggar has the World’s hottest Sculpture Spring Waters and is a holy place for Hindus & Sikhs alike. Return back to Kullu town en-route visiting the famous Kullu Shawl Industry. And late evening catches the Volvo from Kullu to Delhi overnight Journey in Car.', '2019-10-10 13:08:56', '2019-10-10 17:08:56'),
